#doc (Page) "Docs" =>

Documentation will live here as the project grows.

The intent of this section is to hold technical material that should not be mixed into the landing page or grant administration pages. Likely future topics include:

* project status summaries
* track-specific documentation
* specifications and artefact descriptions
* methodology and verification notes
* curated ecosystem references

For now, the current public project information is organized under [Project](/project/), [Grants](/grants/), and [Resources](/resources/).
